CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. A12 reads: "Beauty Contestants - One of these young ladies will be chosen as "Miss Beauty Week" when the Beauty Shop Owners and Beauticians hold their silver anniversary ball at the Sherwyn Hotel, May 12.  Front: Geraldine Wright; second row, Barbara Burwell, Cheryl Banks and Mattie Wages.  Standing: Betty Mabry, Juanita Harper, Mary Sims, Jackie Atkins and Bonnie Carter."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of "Miss Beauty Week" contestants, front row: Geraldine Wright; second row: Barbara Burwell, Cheryl Banks, and Mattie Wages; standing: Betty Mabry, Juanita Harper, Mary Sims, Jackie Atkins and Bonnie Carter, posed in interior with linoleum floor, horizontal format
